snippet.title: Upheaveal Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Upheaveal!

Upheaveal is A physics-based 3D multiplayer party game where players pick up and throw objects in the environment to be the last one standing. Pick from a variety of interstellar champions and duke it out in arenas that span the ages, throwing anything and everything you can get your hands all to cause Upheaveal.

Songs used in the Trailer

Edvard Grieg - Morning

Robotertanz by Shane Ivers - https://www.silvermansound.com

Follow Upheaveal on Social Media

Twitter: https://twitter.com/UpheavealGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Upheaveal-100382802644719
